### Audit & Compliance Logger Service - manual API tests
### base url
@host = http://localhost:8083

### log ekleme 1 - ingestion basarili
POST {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingId": "ad63d65d-4c87-4cb4-a54d-ad14afe2bcd7",
  "userId": "ingestion-service",
  "action": "INGEST_RAW",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "details": "Data received and sent to rabbitmq"
}

### log ekleme 2 - python maskeledi
POST {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingId": "ad63d65d-4c87-4cb4-a54d-ad14afe2bcd7",
  "userId": "anonymization-service",
  "action": "DATA_MASKED",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "details": "PII data masked and saved to mongo"
}

### log ekleme 3 - arastirmaci girdi
POST {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingId": "TRK-2002",
  "userId": "researcher-42",
  "action": "RESEARCHER_ACCESS",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "details": "Researcher queried anonymized metrics"
}

### log ekleme 4 - supheli durum / anomali
POST {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingId": "TRK-2002",
  "userId": "unknown-client",
  "action": "RESEARCHER_ACCESS",
  "status": "ANOMALY",
  "details": "Unauthorized access blocked"
}

### log ekleme 5 - validation hatası / patlayan durum
POST {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingId": "TRK-3003",
  "userId": "ingestion-service",
  "action": "INGEST_RAW",
  "status": "FAILED",
  "details": "Validation failed, bad format"
}

### SORGULAR

### hepsini getir
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs

### sadece anomalileri getir
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs/filter/anomalies

### tek bir trackingId provenance (timestamp artan)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit/logs/ad63d65d-4c87-4cb4-a54d-ad14afe2bcd7

### genel kvkk / uyumluluk raporu
GET {{host}}/api/v1/audit/compliance-report
